Simple and nonobstructive Jinja2 integration with Django.

Provides:
- Template engine backend for Jinja2
- Automatic context processors (request, user, etc.)
- Custom filters and globals (url, static, now, etc.)
- Easy migration from Django templates

Useful for projects that want to use Jinja2 templates alongside
Django's built-in template system.

Requires: Django >= 3.2, Jinja2 >= 2.11

WWW: https://github.com/niwinz/django-jinja
